Package: RDesk
Title: Native Desktop App Framework for R
Version: 1.0.0
Authors@R: 
    person("Janakiraman", "G",
           email = "janakiraman.bt@gmail.com",
           role = c("aut", "cre"),
           comment = c(ORCID = "0000-0001-6050-2318"))
Description: A comprehensive framework for building native Windows desktop 
    applications using R and WebView2. RDesk provides a robust R6-based 
    event loop, asynchronous background task management via mirai/callr, 
    and a native Win32 message bridge for seamless R-to-UI communication 
    without listening ports or network overhead. It allows R developers 
    to create professional, standalone desktop tools with modern web-based 
    user interfaces while maintaining a pure R backend.
